rogue 3.6.3 + bugfixes + changes
================================
                                                               --+-----------
   this began from a rogue3.6.3-src.tar.gz and is mostly for   |............|
historical interest. the code has been updated to compile on   |............|
modern systems without errors, plus bugfixes and other minor   |.........?..|
tweaks where deemed necessary. the GNUisms have been removed   |........H...|
from the Makefile                                              +............|
                                                               |.....*...@..|
    make                                                       --+-----------
    ./rogue

the documentation has been consolidated into rogue.6; copy this into a
suitable MANPATH directory (e.g. /usr/local/share/man/man6) and then run

    man 6 rogue

the wizard mode PASSWD can be changed via crypt(3); set this in rogue.h

    $ perl -E 'say crypt shift, "mT"' Hunter2
    mT6wyq.jl007.

Level: 1  Gold: 0      Hp: 12(12)  Str: 16  Ac: 6   Exp: 1/0
